GateDocument.TextWithNodes: We decided to try this place last night because we noticed that it had some interesting things on the menu aside from the usual rolls -- live scallop sashimi, duck breast nigiri with foie gras, panko mussels -- but none of these were particularly great or worth the sticker price.
